Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:43.57,HERE THE WORLD,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)} Vertes-Manches était mon bonheur,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:49.87,HERE THE WORLD,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an8}Greensleeves was my heart of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:49.87,HERE THE WORLD,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)} Vertes-Manches était mon cœur d'or,
